* I'm sorry for my intrusion when you wanted to find a name for the baby and to what I said about the Romans.I left my angryness dominate me and forgot respect...Quinn,I accept you as my athelfi as long as you are true to your Amazon self and don't invite your father to a family meeting! Quinn, Ainia, I would be glad to see your joining but I have to go, Ainia, I hope to return to the qasatour and see your baby.If I quit Themiskyra, it's to fight the band of assassins who spread terror through our Nation, I'm ready to find my place, to find my way. My way is to fight to protect my athelfi.I'm sorry to have to go, I'll have to pass Sarmatia...I'll return, I promise, as soon as possible...* She gives an amethyst necklace to Ainia* Take it, it's my gift for the baby...that necklace belonged to my mother and have a great value for me...I kept it preciously, it remembered me my mother, made me strong even in the worst situations.It'll protect the baby<br>
